/>\n<br />\n撳入呢度揀你個地區，有埋地圖帶你去票站<br />\n<a href=\"https://legco2020.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flegco2020.com%2F&d=LWtkxptWC%2F4RDCuqQUibmhSGsERVwMiaoyLN1PNQjS0%3D&h=ffd1e84a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://legco2020.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n民意嘅展現永遠係最有效嘅抗爭<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46da49fae4cf3fa361aad2e003a3d151f617050c","tid":2100462,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T14:32:16.000Z","msg":"大家快啲去 down 定呢個 app 去投票 <br />\n#普及投票 4.0 #初選<br />\n<br />\nAndroid<br />\n<br />\n普及投票 4.0<br />\n<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.popvote.voter\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.popvote.voter&d=LWtkxptWC%2F4RDCuqQUibmhSGsERVwMiaoyLN1PNQjS0%3D&h=6f2d52eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.popvote.voter</a><br />\n<br />\n==============<br />\n<br />\niphone如果上唔切架就會連去網站度投<br />\n<br />\n===============<br />\n<br />\n投票須知及流程<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/hJzDNdnFeWLef0ZR069Ta5X-T5Q=/765x890/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3DAAVGWCWLJIOFU2VVC2PVO7SQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FhJzDNdnFeWLef0ZR069Ta5X-T5Q%3D%2F765x890%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3DAAVGWCWLJIOFU2VVC2PVO7SQ.gif&h=bc2d84df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n===============<br />\n<br />\n7月11,12日（六，日）<br />\n0900-2100<br />\n去票站投票<br />\n<br />\n無論你點投, 投比邊個<br />\n<br />\n撳入呢度揀你個地區，有埋地圖帶你去票站<br />\n<a href=\"https://legco2020.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flegco2020.com%2F&d=LWtkxptWC%2F4RDCuqQUibmhSGsERVwMiaoyLN1PNQjS0%3D&h=ffd1e84a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://legco2020.com/</a